        <img class="product-item-img mx-auto d-flex rounded img-fluid mb-3 mb-lg-0" src="../img/products-02.jpg" alt="123">
        <div class="product-item-description d-flex ml-auto">
          <div class="bg-faded p-5 rounded">
            <p class="mb-0">That in terms of Sections 2, 7, 8 and 14 of the Local Government : Municipal Property Rates Act 6
